videos.description: Gary Trent Jr. drains a wide-open triple from the left corner in the first half against NC State.
videos.headline: Trent hits first 3-pointer for Duke

videos.description: Trevon Duval denies NC State's Braxton Beverly's at the rim and they find Grayson Allen at the other end who slams it in for the Blue Devils.
videos.headline: Duke redeems themselves after turnover

videos.description: Lavar Batts Jr. sends a nice pass in transition to Lennard Freeman who rises up and slams it in the first half against Duke.
videos.headline: NC State's Batts feeds Freeman for two-handed jam

videos.description: Gary Trent Jr. knocks the ball away and Trevon Duval goes coast-to-coast for an easy layup plus the foul.
videos.headline: Duval creates 3-point play

videos.description: Trevon Duval sends a perfect bounce pass to Marvin Bagley III who scores the basket and draws the foul for a 3-point play.
videos.headline: Duval dishes to Bagley for and-1

videos.description: Allerik Freeman dishes to Abdul-Malik Abu, who rises above Marvin Bagley III for an aggressive jam in the second half.
videos.headline: NC State's Abu dunks over Bagley.

videos.description: Trevon Duval throws a long pass to Marvin Bagley III who elevates up and throws it down.
videos.headline: Duval feeds Bagley for alley-oop jam

videos.description: Allerik Freeman passes over Duke defenders and Omer Yurtseven finishes at the rim with an aggressive slam.
videos.headline: NC State's Freeman links with Yurtseven for the flush

videos.description: Marvin Bagley III intercepts the ball and goes coast-to-to-coast for a monster finish at the rim in the second half.
videos.headline: Bagley steals and jams

videos.description: NC State's Allerik Freeman speeds down the court and finds Abdul-Malik Abu who finishes with a two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Abu beats Duke's defense for an easy dunk

videos.description: Braxton Beverly drives to get past Duke's defenders and lays it in to extend the Wolfpack's lead to 75-66 with less than 10 minutes left in the game.
videos.headline: Beverly puts on the moves to keep NC State ahead

videos.description: With less than 5 minutes left and Duke trailing, Grayson Allen finds Gary Trent Jr. who banks the layup to make it a one-possession game against NC State.
videos.headline: Trent's layup shrinks Duke's deficit

videos.description: Torin Date gets the inbounds pass and drains an unbelievable 3-pointer while drawing the foul to put NC State ahead 90-80 on Duke late.
videos.headline: NC State's Dorn sinks dagger on Duke

videos.description: Immediately after NC State beats No. 2 Duke 96-85, the court fills up with excited fans surrounding coaches and players
videos.headline: Students rush court after NC State upsets Duke

videos.description: Omer Yurtseven leads NC State past No. 2 Duke with 16 points and believes this signifies a new era for the NC State team.
videos.headline: NC State's Yurtseven overjoyed by win
